libsigc++: libsigc++ (Callback Framework for C++)
libsigc++:
libsigc++: libsigc++ implements a typesafe callback system for standard C++. It
libsigc++: allows you to define signals and to connect those signals to any
libsigc++: callback function, either global or a member function, regardless of
libsigc++: whether it is static or virtual.
libsigc++:
libsigc++:
libsigc++: More information at: http://libsigc.sourceforge.net/
libsigc++:
